      • getIdentifier

        EntityIdentifier getIdentifier()
        Get the identifier that this packet is acting on. This will be null for entity destroy packets
        Returns:
        the identifier of the entity being changed by this packet

      • setIdentifier

        void setIdentifier(EntityIdentifier identifier)
        Set the identifier that this packet is acting on. Null values will be ignored, and the underlying packet will not change.
        Parameters:
        identifier - the identifier of the entity being changed by this packet.
